 also been a board member of endeavororg which supports highimpact entrepreneurs in developing countries and which tom friedman calls the best antipoverty program of all recognizing the necessity for continuous research and development of cutting edge sustainabilityrelated technology mr swette has established the swette strategic investment fund at asu the swette strategic investment fund is intended to play a project and program development role for the julie ann wrigley global institute of sustainability through the identification of specific technological approaches poised for scientific breakthroughs the fund will target projects of three to five year duration that require a reliable stream of pilot results in order to successfully compete for larger federal and industrial grants   bs economics arizona state university contact us facebook twitter linkedinyoutubevimeorss contribute solve programs partnerships what asu is doing campus engage events what you can do contact us internal resources educate school of sustainability education resources news research expert search all research research themes sustainability scientists  scholars asu is  in the us for innovation copyright  trademark accessibility privacy jobs emergency contact asu brian swette  sweet earth enlightened foods  to blog home from the blog brian swette brian t swette  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in brian t swette former board member at carecom inc view full profile are you brian t swette claim your profile   sign up for equilar atlas and view brian t swettes full profile with equilar atlas you can identify corporate executives in brian t swettes network and community follow changes in brian t swettes employment and moneyinmotion connect with brian t swette through your network of contacts brian t swettes executive work history current board member carecom inc past to view brian t swettes complete executive work history sign up 