find quality sources for help formerly ebays chief operating officer brian oversaw that companys international expansion marketing and customer support that made ebay the most accessible and successful ecommerce site on the internet he was instrumental in expanding ebay into new product categories such as used cars and he improved the consumer interface creating features like buy it now which allows consumers to buy auction items at a set price prior to joining ebay brian was executive vice president and chief marketing officer for the pepsicola company during his year tenure he was responsible for the worldwide marketing and advertising efforts for all pepsicola brands and brought lipton iced tea aquafina and the starbucks frappuccino® coffee drink to the pepsi network additionally he oversaw business strategy brand architecture and new product activity and helped introduce popular advertising campaigns including the generation next equity he also directed the marketing of mountain dew making it the fastestgrowing beverage with  billion in sales previously brian worked as a brand manager at procter  gamble he is a trustee at the arizona state universitys global institute of sustainability and a board member of endeavor which helps high impact entrepreneurs in developing markets brian holds a bachelors degree in economics from arizona state university company about us investor relations sheilas blog help safety center careers popular topics babysitters nannies child care housekeepers tutors join us on carecom in my town atlanta austin baltimore boston chicago cincinnati cleveland dallas denver detroit houston indianapolis kansas city los angeles miami minneapolis new york orlando philadelphia phoenix pittsburgh portland sacramento salt lake city san antonio san diego san francisco san jose seattle st louis tampa virginia beach washington dc discover homepay℠  nanny tax help list your business carework  employee benefits programs terms of use privacy policy care dire